item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Kenneth Lofton Jr is a 19-year-old basketball athlete from Port Arthur, Texas. He currently plays for the Memphis Grizzlies of the NBA. Moreover, Lofton Jr. plays for the team under a dual deal with the Memphis Hustle of the NBA G League. He competed for the Conference USA’s Louisiana Tech Bulldogs throughout his college career. As of 2022, he has been named to the Conference USA first team twice, the first time as a sophomore.

item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Florida’s Wyatt Langford sits at No. 2 on my latest MLB Draft rankings, and was No. 1 earlier in the year before he fouled a ball off a bad place, which kept him out for two weeks but didn’t require surgery. He came back incredibly quickly and hasn’t let up at the plate, reaching base four more times when I saw him against Florida State at the Triple-A ballpark in Jacksonville on May 2.

item.title: Lawsuit Settlement: Prince Andrew Reported To Sell His $23 Million Ski-Resort Chalet
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: The couple has an $8 million debt on their Swiss home they took a mortgage for. The two bought the chalet in 2014 in Verbier, Switzerland (it was planned to be a long-term family investment) for $23 million. Yet, they didn't pay off the share of the home by the end of December 2019 - $6 million was to be paid in cash as a deposit. But the couple agreed with the original house owner to pay $8 million with interest.
